Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.81,0:00:05.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就完成了～
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.73,0:00:07.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  睡得還真沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:10.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定是因為演羅密歐累了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.04,0:00:15.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  澪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.13,0:00:17.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.88,0:00:19.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.30,0:02:00.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.26,0:02:03.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪打人啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.08,0:02:05.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了讓澪不緊張嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.18,0:02:09.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫得太多了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.53,0:02:11.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫得越多就越有效果嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.91,0:02:14.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命線也幫你畫粗了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.02,0:02:34.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.99,0:02:36.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.77,0:02:38.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都好好特訓過了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.62,0:02:39.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.86,0:02:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像平時一樣來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.50,0:02:42.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.41,0:02:44.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  那上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.45,0:02:45.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.57,0:02:47.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:48.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.51,0:02:49.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最棒的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.81,0:02:50.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結束後吃蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.33,0:02:53.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.38,0:02:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:09.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.79,0:03:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:13.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.40,0:03:22.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  準備就緒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:26.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶  這是第三次學園祭的演唱會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:27.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.96,0:03:30.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前的第一次可是非常緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.16,0:03:32.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩年前…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.24,0:03:34.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不  我不是說那件事…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.07,0:03:36.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你看  去年就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.88,0:03:40.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又是發燒又是把吉太忘在家裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.74,0:03:41.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.23,0:03:44.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時真是太對不起大家了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.54,0:03:44.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不不…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.64,0:03:46.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓大家久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.40,0:03:48.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著是櫻高祭最受注目的節目  
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.49,0:03:50.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後茶會的演唱會
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.78,0:03:53.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把難度提高啊  和
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:55.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要  我不要那樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.99,0:03:57.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的  小澪
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.03,0:04:00.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,俗話說有二就有三
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:01.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…你這不是在鼓勵她
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:02.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.61,0:04:03.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.28,0:04:04.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.78,0:04:15.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.93,0:04:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:27.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.27,0:04:30.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家和我們穿著一樣的T恤
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.85,0:04:34.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼各位  獻上盛大的掌聲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.57,0:04:35.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.70,0:04:37.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下  和  這是在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.32,0:04:41.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說只是微薄之力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.43,0:04:44.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我怎麼說也是澪粉絲俱樂部的繼任會長
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:45.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:47.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家穿的T恤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷…冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.14,0:04:53.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,T恤是山中老師做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.09,0:04:56.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後在演唱會之前一起發給大家的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.95,0:04:59.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小佐和  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:01.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.21,0:05:03.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.68,0:05:04.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
