Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:43.40,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是小紬
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:46.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家今天能來看我們的表演
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.39,0:12:48.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起來  紬～！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.81,0:12:51.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.76,0:12:54.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,樂團實在太快樂了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.24,0:12:56.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也非常快樂！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬  冷靜一點
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:03.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬泡的茶非常好喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.36,0:13:05.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我每天都在期待哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.38,0:13:06.57,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想嘗嘗～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.06,0:13:10.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨時都可以來活動室  我們很歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.08,0:13:15.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動室裡還有小豬  歡迎大家來看它
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小豬是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.37,0:13:18.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小豬啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.89,0:13:20.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一種叫做豬鼻龜的烏龜
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.27,0:13:23.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻子像豬豬一樣很可愛哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.15,0:13:24.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.10,0:13:26.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…對
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.68,0:13:27.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是吉他手梓喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.47,0:13:32.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:33.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事  不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.48,0:13:40.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…我是中野梓  請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.72,0:13:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓～
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:47.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然梓喵還只是二年級  但吉他的技術相當好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.73,0:13:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是讓梓喵教我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梓喵  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.09,0:13:55.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.13,0:13:58.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來輪到鼓手小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.04,0:14:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們輕音社的社長
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:07.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…感謝各位今天能來觀看我們輕音社的演奏
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.77,0:14:08.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲！小律！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.88,0:14:10.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:13.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那接著演奏下一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.62,0:14:13.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:14.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好短
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.46,0:14:16.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.31,0:14:16.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,行了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.92,0:14:19.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.48,0:14:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以上  接著是下一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.61,0:14:23.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  還沒介紹自己呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:25.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  對了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.81,0:14:27.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後是吉他手小唯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.40,0:14:29.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.13,0:14:35.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯雖然和看上去的感覺一樣  慢悠悠又迷糊糊的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.45,0:14:38.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實一直竭盡全力在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.73,0:14:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給身邊的人注入活力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.22,0:14:44.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一位非常可靠的前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.19,0:14:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  怎麼了？出什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.35,0:14:50.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  快開始下一曲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.41,0:14:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  憂！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.51,0:14:55.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.92,0:14:57.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看我了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.60,0:14:59.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然會看了…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.19,0:15:00.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.27,0:15:02.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後茶會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.31,0:15:04.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後茶會
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.77,0:15:24.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  接下來是最後一首曲子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.29,0:15:27.26,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎～  再繼續嘛～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:31.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然還想多演奏一些的…可是時間有限
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.76,0:15:31.30,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.22,0:15:33.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很精彩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.56,0:15:34.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.83,0:15:35.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後～
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.11,0:15:37.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們倒是把茶會兩字加上啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.51,0:15:45.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天  謝謝大家
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.19,0:15:48.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山中老師  謝謝你的T恤！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.05,0:15:52.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和和  平日受你照顧了！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.94,0:15:55.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憂  小純  謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.90,0:15:57.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位同學們  謝謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.84,0:15:58.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.74,0:15:59.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你最棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.41,0:16:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.63,0:16:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小豬謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.18,0:16:03.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活動室謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.66,0:16:04.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太謝謝你！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.21,0:16:08.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家大家  真的謝謝你們！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.64,0:16:13.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後茶會…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.48,0:16:15.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠  永遠…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.39,0:16:17.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是放學後！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.27,0:16:19.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:20.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.62,0:16:25.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼請聽最後最後一曲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.40,0:16:27.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「U & I」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:47.44,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミがいないと　なんにも　できないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:51.07,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミのごはんが食べたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:56.59,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,もしキミが帰ってきたら　とびっきりの笑顔で
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:17:00.50,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱きつくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:05.54,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミがいないと謝れないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:09.76,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミの声が聞きたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:14.65,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミの笑顔が見れれば
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:18.95,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,それだけで　いいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:23.52,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミが　そばにいるだけで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:28.38,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつも勇気もらってた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:32.92,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,いつまででも一緒にいたい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:37.20,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,この気持ちを伝えたいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:41.82,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晴の日にも　雨の日も
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:46.67,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,キミは　そばにいてくれた
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:55.04,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目を閉じれば　キミの笑顔　輝いてる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.16,0:16:47.44,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你我什麼也做不到
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.67,0:16:51.07,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想吃你做的飯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.19,0:16:56.59,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當你回來就會綻放笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.81,0:17:00.50,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊緊將你擁抱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:05.54,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有你我連道歉都不行
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:09.76,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想聽你的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.96,0:17:14.65,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能夠看見你的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.84,0:17:18.95,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就能夠滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.13,0:17:23.52,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有你陪伴在我身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:28.38,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就能充滿勇氣
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.52,0:17:32.92,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望無論何時都在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.08,0:17:37.20,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傾訴這份心情
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.38,0:17:41.82,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論晴天也好雨天也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.97,0:17:46.67,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你總相伴身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.81,0:17:55.04,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊閉雙眼後看到的　是你燦爛的笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.10,0:18:33.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空前絕後…了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.31,0:18:36.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺只是一瞬間啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.52,0:18:42.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,演奏太順利的關係嗎  我基本沒什麼印象了…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.49,0:18:46.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說是被T恤的驚喜吹散了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:49.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是  腦子亂亂的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.93,0:18:53.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  很贊對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是至今為止最棒的演出吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.68,0:19:00.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家的配合也超棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.39,0:19:02.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合上了合上了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:04.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉太也很高興對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.50,0:19:06.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  伊麗莎白也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊麗莎白～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:10.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的穆炭也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.46,0:19:13.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  小梓的吉他叫穆炭啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.83,0:19:15.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs22}Mustang　　　　　{\r}\N因為是野馬  所以就叫穆炭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.82,0:19:20.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說我說  接下來大家幹點什麼好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.68,0:19:22.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我想先吃點蛋糕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.00,0:19:24.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  社費有的是哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.85,0:19:27.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  我都帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.33,0:19:31.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好誒  那先吃這個再想接著要幹什麼吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.67,0:19:34.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來是聖誕派對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.63,0:19:36.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再下來是正月了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.82,0:19:38.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去參拜吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後是下次新歡演出
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.37,0:19:44.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次繼續住學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次把小佐和也叫上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.44,0:19:48.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那真是個好主意哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.29,0:19:51.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到夏天還有空調
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.40,0:19:52.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還能合宿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.02,0:19:55.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好期待哦～再往後…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.18,0:19:58.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯～再往後的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.14,0:20:01.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  沒往後了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.48,0:20:05.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明年的學園祭一定會演出得更好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.31,0:20:08.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想留級嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.59,0:20:10.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經沒有高中的學園祭了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:14.72,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎～那太可惜了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.59,0:20:17.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要不要
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬學姐  不要說任性的話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.42,0:20:23.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯學姐也不要像小孩一樣哭哭啼啼的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.16,0:20:25.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是汗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.81,0:20:33.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,澪～番茄紅素
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.75,0:20:38.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不也在哭鼻子嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.63,0:20:39.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的也只是汗而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.11,0:20:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  紬學姐也擦下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.25,0:20:46.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.60,0:20:47.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.48,0:20:49.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小梓  謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.83,0:20:50.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.84,0:20:57.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬學姐  沒事啦  冷靜點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.03,0:21:02.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣很棒了吧  這樣真的很棒了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.25,0:21:05.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  這樣太棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.18,0:21:08.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家一起演奏  我很幸福！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.07,0:21:11.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.19,0:21:17.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等下  唯  你的鼻涕  鼻涕
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.39,0:21:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紬紬～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.13,0:21:20.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鼻涕～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.19,0:21:25.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,番茄紅素
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.20,0:21:37.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唯她們真的嚇了一跳呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.40,0:21:42.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,震驚T恤作戰大成功！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.40,0:21:43.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.54,0:21:46.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐和子！佐和子！佐和子！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家  辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.51,0:21:49.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.59,0:21:50.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.78,0:22:01.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一臉滿足的表情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.42,0:23:43.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在研究拍畢業照時候的髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.56,0:23:45.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是想照漂亮點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.48,0:23:47.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟是一輩子留念的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.24,0:23:48.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不學習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.26,0:23:50.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭痛？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.51,0:23:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我和平時不一樣哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是還真看不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.93,0:23:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃…和和  我們都相處這麼長時間了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.93,0:24:01.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗…狗  你說狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.16,0:24:03.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.57,0:24:05.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小學的是抿著嘴笑
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.79,0:24:07.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中學的是太過緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.01,0:24:09.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次一定要照漂亮點！


